From 5c8bbe39ffecfa68814d6b46cfe66c2608e0811e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: BeneSys Fix <fix@benesys.in>
Date: Thu, 19 Mar 2026 13:12:08 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] =?UTF-8?q?fix:=20Tab=20navigation=20-=20only=20Qty?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=E2=86=92Rate=E2=86=92Disc%=E2=86=92next=20row,=20never=20jumps?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=20to=20sidebar=20or=20buttons?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Simplified global hook: only auto-select + block sidebar Tab
- Added tabIndex={-1} to all non-input buttons (Save, Search, Tax Type, Remove, etc)
- Added tabIndex={-1} to all sidebar links and logout
- Tab strictly flows: Qty→Rate→Disc%→next row Qty (adds new row on last)
- Matches the expected behavior shown in reference video
---
